  "id": "CHAR_tovin_rusk",
  "label": "Tovin Rusk",
  "description": "This individual is a broad-shouldered adult of working age, with brown eyes set beneath a heavy brow and a jaw thickened by long habit of exertion. Brown hair is kept in a shortknot to clear the face, and bronze skin shows the permanent weathering and ingrained grime typical of yard labor. The hands are notably large, with blunt fingers and old, healed splits at the knuckles. A flattened nose and a small seam-scar along the left cheekbone mark prior mishap without diminishing the overall impression of durable health.",
